  • public final class RelationshipBuilder
extends AbstractMonikerBuilder<IRelationship,RelationshipBuilder>
    Convenience Builder pattern class for creating new IRelationship instances.

    The minimum fields required to define a new instance are:

    • Field.ENTITY_REFERENCE_TYPE
    • Field.REFERENCE_URN_FIELD
    • Field.RELATED_ENTITY_REFERENCE_TYPE
    • Field.RELATED_REFERENCE_URN_FIELD
    • Field.TYPE_FIELD
